                        <title level="a">Bones in Bags: Relics in Syriac Hagiography</title>
                        <title level="m">Syriac Encounters: Papers from the Sixth North American Syriac
                Symposium, Duke University, 26-29 June 2011</title>
                        <title level="s">Eastern Christian Studies</title>
                        <ptr target="http://syriaca.org/bibl/2198"/>
